 下下都大魚大肉   <br />\n<br />\n好浪費 壞少少野都會成部電器唔要  <br />\n<br />\n通常都係老公有錢 老婆係靚女  幾矮幾醜樣都無問題 有錢就有靚女靚老婆 大婆住一座 細婆住二座都無問題"},{"pid":"d4c4586eeb9c5ad51936925892ce0c896f382b36","tid":1903332,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f20998da5721ef3c54c29b6f370f9f8bf67458e7","tid":1903332,"uid":77323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"會買營養快線飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"個人飄啦"},{"pid":"17a31c86e732dcd8b612e89dd10e78b1e3b990f5","tid":1903332,"uid":26353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f20998da5721ef3c54c29b6f370f9f8bf67458e7","tid":1903332,"uid":77323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"會買營養快線飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:42:36.000Z","msg":"啦啦車民<br />\n孭吓公盟包"},{"pid":"64cdf3e2b79dabac163c3df10e9ae750afdd81ca","tid":1903332,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"40af3190d794c7dce035cb6f174d6b92ea50d029","tid":1903332,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0fcc1833c7d7fcd40dbf7acd0b072a495893df02","tid":1903332,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:15:46.000Z","msg":"每幾個月 就有呢啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做緊豪宅保安 答你少少 <br />\n<br />\n都會坐巴士地鐵的士 分別係趕果陣 窮人都會邊屌邊坐巴士地鐵 有錢人就落標加100 快就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都會食大家樂大快活 如果多人排隊 有錢就直接去超貴既餐廳唔洗排 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買野唔會睇價錢  買到岩心水既最緊要 買樓買車都係咁 舊樓蝕讓200萬？no problem 最緊要新單位岩心水"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"又唔係有錢仔，你憑咩答<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T02:42:53.000Z","msg":"反正都唔會有錢仔答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用窮人角度答你 分享返窮人想知既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=